beer.beer_description:
P-A-R-T-Y
Ohhhhh yeah!
We’ve found our rhythm now, the city is humming with activity and our party seems to be right in the smack bang centre of it all.
The room is vibrating with the music, the walls are breathing and the floor is rising and falling like waves. And, if you look really closely, everything is just made of juicy oranges and mandarins. That’s because Phase Three: Over-Falsity has just arrived and it’s brought some juicy goodies with it.
Over-Falsity can be mellow. Over-Falsity can be fruity. Over-Falsity can pack a punch.
Over-Falsity can be anything you need right now, it’s just here to guide you right on into the warm, welcoming night!
